manifest_analysis.title: Launch Mode of Activity (crc64cedd1b956a3e72a4.MainActivity) is not standard.
manifest_analysis.desc: An Activity should not be having the launch mode attribute set to "singleTask/singleInstance" as it becomes root Activity and it is possible for other applications to read the contents of the calling Intent. So it is required to use the "standard" launch mode attribute when sensitive information is included in an Intent.
manifest_analysis.name: Launch Mode of Activity is not standard.

playstore_details.description:
CoinPayments is a comprehensive platform offering storage and payment support for bitcoin and 1,200+ other cryptocurrencies. The CoinPayments mobile app allows you to conveniently store, send, receive and convert your crypto all in one place!

Trusted by over 2.4 million businesses and users across 182 countries, CoinPayments is the ideal choice when it comes to a comprehensive yet easy to use cryptocurrency wallet and payments platform.
“CoinPayments is the everyday crypto platform for your everyday crypto needs”
“The United Nations of Crypto Wallets”
BITCOIN & ALTCOIN WALLETS

CoinPayments provides a secure, reliable and easy to use wallet for bitcoin and each of the 1,200+ altcoins and tokens supported on the platform. Use QR codes, NFC, wallet addresses or $PayByName to deposit or withdraw cryptocurrencies. The CoinPayments App offers safe and dedicated wallets all in one convenient app, including:

•	Bitcoin (BTC) Wallet
•	Ethereum (ETH) Wallet
•	Litecoin (LTC) Wallet
•	Ripple (XRP) Wallet
•	Monero (XMR) Wallet
•	Tron (TRX) Wallet
•	EOS Wallet
•	Dash Wallet
•	Dogecoin (DOGE) Wallet
•	Bitcoin Cash (BCH) Wallet
•	Bitcoin SV (BSV) Wallet
•	Digibyte (DGB) Wallet
•	Komodo (KMD) Wallet
•	Lisk (LSK) Wallet
•	NEO Wallet
•	Qtum Wallet
•	Steem Wallet
•	Waves Wallet
•	NEM (XEM) Wallet
•	ZCash Wallet
•	Stratis (STRAT) Wallet
•	PIVX Wallet
•	ERC20 Token Wallets
•	Many More…

CRYPTOCURRENCY PAYMENTS

Ready to take your crypto game to the next level? CoinPayments has you covered with our crypto payment gateway that supports over 100 coins! You can start accepting crypto payments online within minutes, using any of our pre-built plugins and integrations for all the major ecommerce platforms.

Have a brick and mortar store and want to accept crypto payments? No problem! The CoinPayments mobile app comes with an easy to use Point of Sale (POS) feature that provides real-time exchange rates for 27 fiat currencies, with optional tax and tipping features.

STABLE COIN INTEGRATION

The CoinPayments platform has already integrated 4 of the top stable coins including Tether (USDT), True USD (TUSD), Gemini Dollar (GUSD) and USD Coin (USDC).
With this native integration, businesses can now accept payments directly in the stable coin of their choice. Additionally, businesses and users can reduce the volatility of the cryptocurrencies they are storing by converting them into stable coins.

FEATURES

Some of the features that make the “CoinPayments – Crypto Wallet” app a comprehensive experience include:

- $PayByName – A unique tag that replaces all of your complex coin addresses with one simple name of your choice
- Mobile Point of Sale (POS) – Accept cryptocurrency in person with optional tax and tipping
- Vaulting – Additional layer of security offering secured storage with a time-delayed unlock
- Conversion – Manually or automatically convert one cryptocurrency into many others
- Fiat Settlement – Settle your crypto payments into any of 9 different fiat currencies directly into your bank account
- Payment Forwarding – Instantly forward payments directly to a wallet address of your choice
- 27 Fiat Currency Exchange Rate Calculations

ABOUT COINPAYMENTS

CoinPayments was founded in 2013 as the first altcoin payment solution and has since grown to support payments for bitcoin and over 1,200 altcoins for a userbase of over 2.4 million business and user accounts across 182 countries. The easy to use platform offers prebuilt plugins and integrations for all the major ecommerce platforms, including Shopify, Woocommerce and Magento. With hosted wallets, conversion and fiat settlement functionality, CoinPayments leads the way in furthering the adoption of cryptocurrencies.

Keep in Touch with CoinPayments

Homepage: https://www.coinpayments.net
Latest News: https://blog.coinpayments.net/
Support: https://www.coinpayments.net/supwiz
Twitter: https://twitter.com/CoinPaymentsNET
